&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NHS Benchmarking Network Project Co-ordinator.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a bright, energetic individual to play an integral role in all aspects of benchmarking project delivery for the Network. The ideal candidate will be a confident communicator with a high level of numeracy and the ability to read and interpret data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for delivering excellent customer service assisting members throughout the process, being their first point of contact for project queries. You will have responsibility for co-ordinating project activities, drafting project outputs and, ensure projects are delivered to a high standard and on time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Curiosity and a passion for using data to support improvement in the NHS are the key attributes we are looking for in candidates for this entry level post. We will support you to qualify in Prince2 project management methodology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benchmark Management Consulting runs the NHS Benchmarking Network, a member organisation that develops and delivers national benchmarking and data analytics projects for the NHS. As the leading benchmarking network for health and social care intelligence in the UK, we are proud to support our clients to improve NHS services and deliver the NHS Long Term Plan. In addition to a core annual work programme for members, we also undertake projects and audits commissioned by central NHS bodies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will demonstrate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;degree level education with a minimum BA/BSc 2:2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a passion for working with data to generate insight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ability to meet project deadlines and targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a willingness to develop presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;self-motivation, able to operate proactively and independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a willingness to learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;successful team working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
